%section.section#locations
  .container
    .page-header
      %h2 Locations

    .row
      .col-xs-12.col-sm-6
        %h3 The Awesome Conference Venue

        %p
          %strong Alamo Drafthouse
          %br
          2550 Mission Street
          %br
          San Francisco, California 94110
          %br
          = link_to 'Google Map', 'https://goo.gl/maps/f93dUKY4EzQ2'

        %p
          In typical Alamo Drafthouse style, food and drinks can be had at
          your seat! The staff will take orders and deliver food and beverages
          between talks.

      .col-xs-12.col-sm-6
        %h3 Thursday Happy Hour

        %p
          %strong Eventbrite
          %br
          155 5th St. 7th Floor
          %br
          San Francisco, California 94103
          %br
          = link_to 'Google Map', 'https://goo.gl/maps/gfb4DqM9tDM2'

        %p
          Join us for food, drinks, and mingling Thursday night at 6&ndash;9pm
          to cap off a great first day!
          %strong Thank you Eventbrite for sponsoring!
          RSVP will be required (form coming soon).



%section.section#register
  .container
    .page-header
      %h2 Register

    %p
      %strong
        If you are (or plan to be) a sponsor,
        = link_to 'contact us', '/contact'
        to receive your ticket(s) as defined within your
        = succeed '.' do
          = link_to 'sponsorship level', '/sponsor'

    .embed-responsive.embed-responsive-16by9
      %iframe.embed-responsive-item(src="//eventbrite.com/tickets-external?eid=19886717708&ref=etckt" scrolling="auto" allowtransparency="true")



